</XX>
<CO>Gallup China.
    Carrie Enterprises.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>CNZ  China, Asia.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P8732 Commercial Nonphysical Research.
</IN>
<XX>
Types:-
